response.original_title: Another Man With a Sword, Don't Try to be Stronger Than My Death
response.overview: As always, we breed the plague. "Another man with a sword, don't try to be stronger than my Death" is a video art I shot especially for our album "Minotaur - Ananke" and is a kaleidoscope of my and Zura's body performances.
response.title: Another Man With a Sword, Don't Try to be Stronger Than My Death
